Live the life you choose with Hireup’s app.

Hireup is Australia’s largest NDIS registered online platform. With the app, Hireup clients and disability support workers can find the right support and work easily.

Message on the go

Start conversations with clients and disability support workers. Messages are safe, secure, and kept in one place for your convenience.

Search and view profiles

Search for clients and disability support workers near you. Filter by support types, location, demographics, interests and more.

Manage bookings from start to finish

Create, manage and approve bookings. We take care of the rest. All support workers are employed by Hireup.

Download the app today to provide support or find the right support workers, anytime, anywhere.

creator: Hireup Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Your life, supported

Make your life easier with the Hireup app.

Designed for NDIS participants, account managers, and support workers alike, the app gives you the freedom to connect, book, and manage everything from your phone or tablet —whenever and wherever you need it.

WHAT CAN YOU DO ON THE APP?

Easily browse profiles that suit your needs: Search for support workers or clients near you by support types, location and more to find the right match for you.

Message when you’re on the go: Send and receive messages to easily organise your next booking, keep track of your conversations, and stay connected anytime, anywhere.

Find support and book shifts: Use the job board to post and apply for shifts that suit your needs and schedule.

Add your bookings to your calendar: Effortlessly stay on top of all of your upcoming bookings by adding them directly to your calendar.

Stay in the loop: Enable push notifications so you never miss a message or booking update.

Advance your support career: For support workers, Hireup Academy is just a tap away, giving you easy access to free online training and upskilling resources to achieve your career goals.

IS THE HIREUP APP ACCESSIBLE FOR PEOPLE WITH DISABILITIES?

Hireup is committed to creating an accessible and inclusive experience for everyone. We use community feedback to inform how the app works, as well as leveraging accessibility best practices.
